          <title><![CDATA[Job Description]]></title>
          <content><![CDATA[VCOM Inc. has immediate openings for Fibre Optic Technicians to work in San Jose and surrounding areas.<br/>Applicants must have a minimum of 2 years experience in fibre optic splicing and testing.<br/>We have been in business since 1998 and are privately owned Canadian Contracting Company that offers its' customers a wide range of services from Installations and Service, Construction, Technical, Planning & Design, Fibre Optics, Directional Drilling and much more.<br/>We offer competitive wages, benefits, Employee Retirement Plan and many more other perks.<br/>]]></content>
        </item>
        <item>
          <descriptionId>
            <value><![CDATA[job_requirements]]></value>
          </descriptionId>
          <title><![CDATA[Qualifications]]></title>
          <content><![CDATA[<ul><li>Splice and test various types of fibre optic cable</li><li>Can read system maps</li><li>Can operate all types of splicing and testing equipment</li><li>Must be able to carry and climb a twenty eight foot extension ladder and the ability to work at heights</li><li>Must be well organized and able to work independently and or as part of a team</li><li>Will be required to work in all weather conditions</li><li>Will be required to work weekends and off hours</li></ul>]]></content>
